lead_paragraph: For a moment, just after Yaya Toure's penalty had won the League Cup for Manchester City on Sunday, hero Willy Caballero seemed unaware of what had just transpired in the Wembley final against Liverpool.

headline.print_headline: Jeepers Keepers! Caballero Enjoys Rare Day on City Stage
